src:
Winning numbers drawn in 'Pick 3 Evening' game
04 Nov 2019, 01:08 by The Associated Press
CLEVELAND (AP) _ The winning numbers in Sunday evening's drawing of the Ohio Lottery's "Pick 3 Evening" game were:
8-3-7
(eight, three, seven)
